Date: Tue, 1 May 2018 16:23:10 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] luna-sysservice: Add service file for systemd

In order to get rid of webos-initscripts, add the required files to the components.

Signed-off-by: Herman van Hazendonk <github.com@herrie.org>

---
 files/systemd/luna-sys-service.service | 29 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 29 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 files/systemd/luna-sys-service.service

diff --git a/files/systemd/luna-sys-service.service b/files/systemd/luna-sys-service.service
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..cf9afb7
--- /dev/null
+++ b/files/systemd/luna-sys-service.service
@@ -0,0 +1,29 @@
